text: The haters on $TWTR are multiplying on my thread. Increasingly it is making little sense for me to spend the time to Tweet and offer (for free) some of my ideas and analysis. Frankly, I have no need to increase my presence here for the purpose of expanding my "franchise."

There are simply - on $TWTR - too many sharks in the way of me getting to the nice fish (and having value added disc) So I will take at least a ten day hiatus - I will be back around October 5 - and in the interim I will think about how and whether I will continue to use TWTR
